main event: A 13-year-old student in NE Houston, Texas spotted a black and white disk-shaped object rapidly moving across the horizon to the south on May 5, 1965 at 6:15 PM.
interesting points: The object was visible for about 1 minute.
The object had a disk shape and was black and gray in color.
The object was seen moving rapidly across the horizon to the south.
The witness did not report any sound or vapor trail from the object.
The weather was clear at the time of the sighting.
